| 
| Generic model of a Request for an Extract, containing an Extract specification.
| 

class EXTRACT_ACTION_REQUEST
    is_a LOCATABLE

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Identifier of previous `EXTRACT_REQUEST`.
    | 
    prop request_id: OBJECT_REF;

    | 
    | Requested action: `cancel | resend | send new`. Coded by openEHR Terminology
    | group `'extract action type'`.
    | 
    prop action: DV_CODED_TEXT;

    | 
    prop uid: HIER_OBJECT_ID;


end
